{{ElectionsCO}}
The '''1980 United States Senate election in Colorado''' was held on November 4, 1986. Incumbent Democratic U.S. Senator [[Gary Hart]] won re-election to a second term.

== Major candidates ==
=== Democratic ===
*[[Gary Hart]], incumbent U.S. Senator

=== Republican ===
*Mary Estill Buchanan, [[Colorado Secretary of State]]

